# Fail fast when the active Node.js version is outside `engines.node`.
# Node 25 breaks the native compilation of `macos-alias` (transitive dep of
# `appdmg` → `electron-installer-dmg` → `@electron-forge/maker-dmg`), so the
# Electron DMG build fails opaquely. With `engine-strict=true`, an `npm install`
# on Node 25 errors immediately rather than silently skipping the optional
# `appdmg` install and failing only at `electron-forge make` time.
#
# See: package.json `engines.node`.
engine-strict=true
